---
title: Sticky Ginger Beef and Rice Bowls with Marinated Veggies and Snap Peas
description: This aromatic beef bowl is packed with tangy marinated veggies and fluffy jasmine rice. Drizzle over a tasty Japanese-inspired soy mayo, then stir all the vibrant ingredients together for a classic takeout experience at home!
